+This is the native companion repository for
+[KOReader Stream](https://github.com/yoshitaka420/koreader-stream). It extends
+KOReader's base framework with a libcurl-backed, seekable MuPDF stream for
+bounded WebDAV CBZ/CBR reading, including response validation, in-memory block
+caching, credential cleanup, telemetry, and adversarial tests.
+
+It is intended to be consumed as the main project's `base/` submodule. For the
+complete feature design and build instructions, see the main project README and
+`doc/WebDAV_comic_streaming.md` there.
+
+## Upstream framework
+
+This repository is based on the framework for creating document readers like KOReader,
 an e-ink device oriented reader application for various document formats.

 It uses the MuPDF library (see http://mupdf.com/), djvulibre library,
